fields.value: Vitis riparia and V. rupestris digital leaf images

dsDescriptionValue.value: Digital leaf images used for analysis in Klein et al. (DOI:10.3389/fpls.2017.00373). Included is a spreadsheet (VitisLeafImageInfo.txt) of information about each vine, identifiable by image file name. Vines were harvested from the USDA-ARS Grape Genetics Research Unit Germplasm Reserve in Geneva, NY. PI number corresponds to their identification system.
